At my place I</i>

00:27.794 --> 00:30.035
<i>♪ Out I go with my Joe or John or Billy N'</i>

00:30.196 --> 00:31.470
- Yes.
- Let's go.

00:31.631 --> 00:32.803
- Let's go!
- Come on, Jane.

00:33.233 --> 00:34.371
Yes.

00:34.534 --> 00:36.946
Attagirl. Yes! Ha-ha.

00:37.270 --> 00:39.147
I did it. Finally, I won.

00:39.305 --> 00:40.978
No celebrating.
I beat you by a foot.

00:41.141 --> 00:43.246
No, no, no, Daddy.
You know that I won.

00:43.410 --> 00:46.016
Won, my ass.
I could have smoked a cigarette waiting.

00:46.346 --> 00:48.849
You know, you shouldn't lie.
It sets a bad example.

00:49.015 --> 00:50.016
Oh, you two.

00:50.183 --> 00:52.424
Chad, the apple does not
fall far from the tree.

00:52.585 --> 00:53.723
Chad, who won that race?

00:53.887 --> 00:55.628
This is strictly Hollander business.

00:55.789 --> 00:58.497
- Reenie, let me buy you a juice.
- Oh, such a gentleman.

00:58.658 --> 01:01.070
Yeah. Put it on Gordy's tab.

01:01.227 --> 01:02.228
All right.

01:02.395 --> 01:05.171
Well, they asked me
to audition for The Philadelphia Story.

01:05.331 --> 01:07.743
Mm! You should. As Tracy Lord?

01:07.901 --> 01:10.814
- We'll be in front to cheer you on.
- You don't cheer at a play.

01:11.271 --> 01:14.218
But it is all at night,
and then I wouldn't be home for Daddy...

01:14.374 --> 01:17.514
-...after his day at work.
- Wasn't your goal to retire at 50, Daddy?

01:17.677 --> 01:19.657
And that's, what, five years away?

01:19.813 --> 01:21.224
Yes, exactly.

01:21.381 --> 01:23.486
Now I have to wait until
your idiot brother...

01:23.650 --> 01:26.187
...can prove he won't
run the business into the ground.

01:26.352 --> 01:30.892
I will very likely be an old man unless
I can leave the business to you, Chad.

01:32.892 --> 01:34.030
Well, let's see.

01:34.194 --> 01:36.504
Been at Townley's a month.

01:36.663 --> 01:38.370
How early is too early to resign?

01:41.167 --> 01:43.306
- I'll take that from you, ma'am.
- Oh, I was--

01:43.470 --> 01:44.471
No, she's finished.

01:44.637 --> 01:46.173
Oh, okay.

01:47.974 --> 01:49.248
So finish that story.

